Calculator App built using Titanium SDK

Description: This is a calculator app that has the most basic operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication and division for both whole numbers and decimal numbers.

Intended Devices: iPhone SDK 5+ and Android SDK 2.1 to 4.3 (only).

Built with Titanium SDK version 3.1.1
Machine: MacBook OSX Mountain Lion
Requires Titanium Mobile SDK 1.8.0+

Purpose(s) of this project:
1. Explore and get to know Titanium Studio
2. Install and link iOS and Android SDK from 2.1 to 4.3
3. Play with various UI elements. In this case, one Titanium Textfield and 17 Titanium buttons (Clear, 0-9, plus, minus, multiply, divide, equals and a decimal point).
4. To see the benefits of the idea of "maintain one project and deploy to many platforms."

